SMW+ provides LDAP authentication and some authorization functionality for MediaWiki. "LDAP" stands for ''Lightweight Directory Access Protocol'', which is an application protocol for querying and modifying directory services running over TCP/IP.
<hr>
<b>Note &ndash;</b> In SMW+, LDAP authentication is implemented by the LDAP Authentication MediaWiki extension. For more information, see the [http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:LDAP_Authentication LDAP Authentication Web site].
<hr>